title: President Donald J. Trump Signs H.J.Res. 66 into Law – The White House
content:
Statements & Releases			

		Law & Justice	

Issued on:
May 17, 2017
On Wednesday, May 17, 2017, the President signed into law:H.J.Res. 66, which nullifies the Department of Labor’s rule on Savings Arrangements Established by States for Non-Governmental Employees.
